{"id":477969,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":23}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"毛主席是我们心中的最红最红的太阳　毛泽东思想是我们革命的最亮最亮的灯塔","genre":"","count":"247","ytitle":"","mtitle":"舵手颂","ftitle":"","authors":["沈炳龙"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海化工厂　沈炳龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿人民驾巨舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席是天才的舵手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舵手啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨开重重迷雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闯过险滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕过暗礁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着湍湍激流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风满帆啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈开骇浪惊涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋勇前进!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿人民驾巨舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席是英明的舵手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舵手啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开创人类新纪元，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦奋斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着马列主义的航道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一船凯歌啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色彩霞满天飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报、丰收!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿人民驾巨舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席是伟大的舵手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舵手啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌握革命的航向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼全球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为三十亿人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远战斗啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举伟大红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反帝反修!"}]}